<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title><%= pageTitle %></title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <%- include('partials/navbar', { page }) %>
    <main class="page contact-page">
      <header>
        <h1>We would love to hear from you</h1>
        <p>Tell us about your next project or ask any question — we reply within one business day.</p>
      </header>
      <section class="contact-grid">
        <div class="contact-item">
          <div class="icon-box">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17.657 16.657L13.414 20.9a1.998 1.998 0 01-2.827 0l-4.244-4.243a8 8 0 1111.314 0z" />
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 11a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h2>Visit</h2>
          <p>35 Innovation Avenue<br />Tunis, Tunisia</p>
        </div>
        <div class="contact-item">
          <div class="icon-box">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 5a2 2 0 012-2h3.28a1 1 0 01.948.684l1.498 4.493a1 1 0 01-.502 1.21l-2.257 1.13a11.042 11.042 0 005.516 5.516l1.13-2.257a1 1 0 011.21-.502l4.493 1.498a1 1 0 01.684.949V19a2 2 0 01-2 2h-1C9.716 21 3 14.284 3 6V5z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h2>Call</h2>
          <p><a href="tel:+2165551234">+216 555 1234</a></p>
        </div>
        <div class="contact-item">
          <div class="icon-box">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 8l7.89 5.26a2 2 0 002.22 0L21 8M5 19h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h2>Email</h2>
          <p><a href="mailto:hello@acmesolutions.com">hello@acmesolutions.com</a></p>
        </div>
      </section>
      <section class="contact-flex">
        <div class="contact-form">
          <p class="eyebrow">Tell us more</p>
          <h2>Share a quick brief and we will follow up within 24 hours.</h2>
          <form action="mailto:projects@acmesolutions.com" method="post" enctype="text/plain">
            <div class="form-group">
              <label for="name">Full name</label>
              <div class="input-wrapper">
                <svg class="input-icon" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M16 7a4 4 0 11-8 0 4 4 0 018 0zM12 14a7 7 0 00-7 7h14a7 7 0 00-7-7z" />
                </svg>
                <input type="text" id="name" name="name" placeholder="Amira Ben Said" required>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="form-group">
              <label for="email">Email</label>
              <div class="input-wrapper">
                <svg class="input-icon" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 8l7.89 5.26a2 2 0 002.22 0L21 8M5 19h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z" />
                </svg>
                <input type="email" id="email" name="email" placeholder="amira@example.com" required>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="form-group">
              <label for="budget">Budget range</label>
              <div class="input-wrapper">
                <svg class="input-icon" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8c-1.657 0-3 .895-3 2s1.343 2 3 2 3 .895 3 2-1.343 2-3 2m0-8c1.11 0 2.08.402 2.599 1M12 8V7m0 1v8m0 0v1m0-1c-1.11 0-2.08-.402-2.599-1M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
                </svg>
                <input type="text" id="budget" name="budget" placeholder="e.g. $15k - $30k">
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="form-group">
              <label for="message">Project details</label>
              <div class="input-wrapper">
                <textarea id="message" name="message" rows="4" placeholder="Goals, deadlines, tech stack preferences..."></textarea>
              </div>
            </div>

            <button class="btn btn-block" type="submit">
              <span>Send message</span>
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="btn-icon" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M14 5l7 7m0 0l-7 7m7-7H3" />
              </svg>
            </button>
          </form>
        </div>
        <div class="map-card">
          <img src="https://picsum.photos/id/1011/600/400" alt="Studio space" />
          <div class="map-meta">
            <h3>Studio hours</h3>
            <p>Mon - Fri · 9 AM to 5 PM CET</p>
            <h3>Drop by for a coffee</h3>
            <p>Book a slot and meet the squad IRL.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
      <section class="faq-section">
        <header class="section-header" style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 3rem;">
          <p class="eyebrow">FAQ</p>
          <h2>Common questions</h2>
        </header>
        <div class="faq-grid">
          <div class="faq-item">
            <h3>What is your typical project timeline?</h3>
            <p>Most projects take between 4-8 weeks depending on complexity. We work in 2-week sprints to ensure steady progress.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-item">
            <h3>Do you work with international clients?</h3>
            <p>Absolutely. We have worked with startups and enterprises across Europe, North America, and MENA.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-item">
            <h3>What is your pricing model?</h3>
            <p>We offer both fixed-price project quotes and monthly retainers for ongoing support and growth.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-item">
            <h3>Do you provide post-launch support?</h3>
            <p>Yes, we offer maintenance packages to keep your software secure, up-to-date, and performing well.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
    </main>
    <%- include('partials/footer') %>
    <script src="/js/main.js"></script>
  </body>
</html>
